{"tid":972811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒：金正恩今抵京與習近平會面","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T06:56:10.000Z","uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4280b1e1733f3cf2a1568150e39a858ba8953be","tid":972811,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國又贏！"},{"pid":"493e42ff8e87d2cb616ad1ff0ab15a515c2dbab4","tid":972811,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"路透社今日引述南韓《民族日報》報道，接近朝中關係人士指出，金正恩於今日前赴北京，或與中國國家主席習近平會面。韓聯社則引述消息稱，北韓列車正在接載「高層官員」跨越中朝邊境。<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社消息指出，北韓領導人金正恩疑第四度出訪中國，由於今日下午在中國遼寧丹東車站突然出現大批保安警力，推測可能是金正恩再度出訪，有消息指出，列車可能已經進入中國境內。"},{"pid":"4fd9830ce37f5bf5aee0da75ed9904fd4c33e0ef","tid":972811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"同時貿易談判加見金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c162605b1e291233fde8f033990b6d0d92f3957","tid":972811,"uid":224561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"可能金仔都想叫習大大咪咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b598f3c9442242e0e08a3d548c9d6b6020ae573","tid":972811,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"啦啦隊出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0042e91b7e06b9dae3608a0dcd0e48867efe9cc","tid":972811,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c162605b1e291233fde8f033990b6d0d92f3957","tid":972811,"uid":224561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:56:06.000Z","msg":"可能金仔都想叫習大大